      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing no signs of wear, this motorcar represents the highest standard of automotive excellence. Its flawless exterior finish is complemented by a pristine interior, offering an unrivaled experience for the most discerning driver. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of such distinguished caliber and uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
