    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has been fastidiously maintained with a comprehensive preventative maintenance portfolio, including a documented rod bearing replacement and a full VANOS overhaul using Beisan Systems components to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis is structurally sound, having received a proactive subframe reinforcement to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. Cosmetically, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no evidence of track-use pitting or UV-induced trim degradation. The interior maintains its tactile integrity, with no delamination of the pillars or bolster compression. This is a turn-key mechanical masterpiece with sorted suspension kinematics and a pristine underside.",
